13 An Act relating to daylight saving time; creating the
Wyman West Actual Lock the Clock Act; amending
14 Section 1, Chapter 161, O.S.L. 2024 (25 O.S. Supp.
2024, Section 90.29), which relates to daylight
15 saving standard; mandating year-round standard time;
